video.title: NCIS
video.synopsis: Follow the quirky agents of the NCIS -- the Naval Criminal Investigative Service – as they track down terrorists and other high-profile criminals.

episodes.synopsis: Investigating a Secret Service agent's death aboard Air Force One leads Gibbs and the team to uncover a terrorist's scheme.
episodes.title: Yankee White

episodes.synopsis: When a Marine corporal formerly known for his lucky streak parachutes violently to his death, the agents investigate the men in his unit.
episodes.title: Hung Out to Dry

episodes.synopsis: After a Navy commander's body washes ashore, NCIS must investigate a possible link to two murdered drug runners nearby.
episodes.title: Seadog

episodes.synopsis: A sailor's drowning death points to suicide, but Kate doesn't buy it. Meanwhile, Abby uncovers a link between his ship's crew and a video game.
episodes.title: The Immortals

episodes.synopsis: The body of a Navy officer who vanished in 1994 -- along with $1.2 million -- is discovered in a cargo pod, but the money is nowhere to be found.
episodes.title: The Curse

episodes.synopsis: Two crewmen on a ship overdose on meth but insist they don't use, so Gibbs, Tony and Kate board the carrier to unravel the mystery.
episodes.title: High Seas

episodes.synopsis: When an ecoterrorist cell targets a submarine with an inside job, Gibbs and the team must determine which crew member is the cell's plant.
episodes.title: Sub Rosa

episodes.synopsis: A sailor's death from ingesting emeralds leads the agents to Guantanamo Bay, where they must thwart a terrorist's plot to kill one of his own.
episodes.title: Minimum Security

episodes.synopsis: A Marine killed on a covert CIA mission apparently phones his wife, forcing NCIS to determine whether his death -- or the call -- was a hoax.
episodes.title: Marine Down

episodes.synopsis: A woman who's been buried alive emerges from a shallow grave with no memory of who she is, but certain a bomb is going to detonate on a Navy ship.
episodes.title: Left for Dead

episodes.synopsis: After a CIA employee witnesses the murder of a Navy lieutenant who was testing a high-tech device, the agents try to determine why he was killed.
episodes.title: Eye Spy

episodes.synopsis: When a severed leg with a Semper Fi tattoo is found, the agents try to identify who the limb belongs to, leading to a case from two years earlier.
episodes.title: My Other Left Foot

episodes.synopsis: When a sniper kills two Marine recruiters, the agents must find the culprit before he strikes again.
episodes.title: One Shot, One Kill

episodes.synopsis: With no apparent suspects or motive, the agents struggle to determine why a serial killer is targeting the officers at a naval base.
episodes.title: The Good Samaritan

episodes.synopsis: When his former commanding officer goes AWOL from Iraq, Gibbs must clear him of absconding with millions of dollars.
episodes.title: Enigma

episodes.synopsis: When a gun-toting terrorist takes Ducky, Gerald and Kate hostage, Gibbs and Tony must determine the man's ties and thwart his efforts.
episodes.title: Bête Noire

episodes.synopsis: A petty officer's death at a rave leads the agents into an investigation that points to possible kickbacks, a femme fatale and practical jokes.
episodes.title: The Truth Is Out There

episodes.synopsis: When a former Navy SEAL convicted of murdering his wife escapes from Leavenworth, the agents must track him down before he seeks deadly vengeance.
episodes.title: Unsealed

episodes.synopsis: When a fellow NCIS agent is murdered while investigating a cold case, the team vows to solve the mystery and catch his killer.
episodes.title: Dead Man Talking

episodes.synopsis: The case of a missing Marine leads Gibbs, Tony and Kate to discover that a serial killer is on the loose.
episodes.title: Missing

episodes.synopsis: A Marine's gruesome death leads the agents to a Marine base boxing ring, an agency sting and a black market for assault weapons.
episodes.title: Split Decision

episodes.synopsis: When a Navy SEAL dies while training for a critical mission, the agents have less than 48 hours to find his killer or the operation could be stalled.
episodes.title: A Weak Link

episodes.synopsis: The Hamas operative who held some of the team hostage months earlier resurfaces to kidnap Kate and shoot down the president's helicopter.
episodes.title: Reveille

episodes.synopsis: When the wife and blind 9-year-old daughter of a Navy captain are kidnapped, Gibbs and his team face a unique challenge.
episodes.title: See No Evil

episodes.synopsis: The team is called in to investigate when the decomposed body of a woman in a wedding dress is found in a cell beneath abandoned military housing.
episodes.title: The Good Wives Club

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team is called in to investigate when a perfectly functioning Marine helicopter is found in the middle of a crop circle.
episodes.title: Vanished

episodes.synopsis: When a woman dressed in a Navy uniform is found raped and murdered, Ducky spots a connection to an old case.
episodes.title: Lt. Jane Doe

episodes.synopsis: When the NCIS team finds the remains of an undercover FBI agent on a Marine firing range, they suspect they've stumbled onto a Mafia dumping ground.
episodes.title: The Bone Yard

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team is at odds with an FBI agent while trying to protect an Iraq War veteran and her family from a group of terrorists.
episodes.title: Terminal Leave

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs and his team must clear the name of an elderly Marine who confesses that he murdered his best friend nearly 60 years ago.
episodes.title: Call of Silence

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs and his team investigate the mysterious death of a Navy commander who, after successful open heart surgery, seemingly bursts into flames.
episodes.title: Heart Break

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs and his team are called to the scene when a Marine's wife kills an intruder who tried to rape her.
episodes.title: Forced Entry

episodes.synopsis: The team must work together to find Tony when he disappears during an undercover operation posing as an escaped convict.
episodes.title: Chained

episodes.synopsis: When the body of a missing Navy officer is dredged up from a lake, the NCIS team must determine whether the death was an accident or foul play.
episodes.title: Black Water

episodes.synopsis: When a telemarketer overhears a murder while making a call, the NCIS team works with local homicide detectives find out who wanted the victim dead.
episodes.title: Doppelganger

episodes.synopsis: As he reassembles the pieces of three bodies found stuffed in barrels months ago, Ducky is shocked when he discovers their identities.
episodes.title: The Meat Puzzle

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs gives McGee a shot at running a case when the NCIS team investigates a woman's claim that she witnessed the murder of a sailor.
episodes.title: Witness

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team investigates when a Marine records his own murder on video as he falls off a cliff.
episodes.title: Caught on Tape

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team investigates the bizarre death of a female petty officer who is found brutally murdered in the bed of a dance club bartender.
episodes.title: Pop Life

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team investigates when a sailor in Washington, D.C., receives a package from Paraguay containing a pair of blue eyeballs.
episodes.title: An Eye for an Eye

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team investigates when a petty officer who recently returned from duty is found dead backstage at a local bikini contest.
episodes.title: Bikini Wax

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team investigates when a petty officer commits suicide after being institutionalized for a nervous breakdown.
episodes.title: Conspiracy Theory

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs and the team head back to school when a Marine in an ROTC program is found murdered on a college campus.
episodes.title: Red Cell

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs and the team work to clear the name of a Navy medic killed in Iraq who was suspected of committing a murder in his hometown.
episodes.title: Hometown Hero

episodes.synopsis: When a letter sealed with a kiss is delivered to NCIS, Tony assumes it's for him and opens it, releasing a mysterious powder into the squad room.
episodes.title: S.W.A.K.

episodes.synopsis: NCIS pays the ultimate price when a hunt for a terrorist assassination team turns deadly for one team member.
episodes.title: Twilight

episodes.synopsis: As the season opens, the NCIS team is struggling to deal with Kate Todd's death, and Gibbs is determined to seek out and destroy her killer.
episodes.title: Kill Ari: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The man responsible for Kate's death is playing terror games with members of the NCIS team, strengthening Gibbs's resolve to find and kill him.
episodes.title: Kill Ari: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: A serial killer Gibbs arrested years ago turns out to have an accomplice, which is all the more alarming when Agent Cassidy goes missing.
episodes.title: Mind Games

episodes.synopsis: A dead Marine found inside a Civil War-era tomb at the Smithsonian appears to have been buried alive. Meanwhile, Ziva must prove her worth.
episodes.title: Silver War

episodes.synopsis: When the team investigates the murder of a petty officer gunned down on the freeway, they discover someone stole the officer's identity.
episodes.title: Switch

episodes.synopsis: A Marine sergeant's wife who runs a live sex website suddenly vanishes, and preliminary evidence suggests that her murder was broadcast online.
episodes.title: The Voyeur's Web

episodes.synopsis: While investigating the kidnapping of a lieutenant commander who had been working on a classified project, the team looks after his young son.
episodes.title: Honor Code

episodes.synopsis: When two married assassins who were planning a hit at a Marine Corps ball die in an accident, Tony and Ziva pose as the couple to investigate further.
episodes.title: Under Covers

episodes.synopsis: When body parts are found on a Marine base and all evidence suggests that Tony is the murderer, the NCIS team frantically works to clear his name.
episodes.title: Frame-Up

episodes.synopsis: When McGee shoots an undercover detective in an alley, Gibbs wonders about the detective's reason for being there in the first place.
episodes.title: Probie

episodes.synopsis: Soon after a supermodel dies of an overdose on a Marine base where she was filming a reality TV show, the team is perplexed by two related cases.
episodes.title: Model Behavior

episodes.synopsis: During a search for illegal weapons in a naval shipyard, Tony and Ziva get ambushed and find themselves locked inside a container.
episodes.title: Boxed In

episodes.synopsis: The team looks into the abduction of a Navy officer in charge of a nuclear weapons shipment, learning she also worked to combat online pedophilia.
episodes.title: Deception

episodes.synopsis: When two Marine wives, both Korean-born, are found murdered, the NCIS team investigates and discovers ties to a sleeper cell and North Korea.
episodes.title: Light Sleeper

episodes.synopsis: When a human head is found, Abby traces it to a deceased Navy captain, only to learn that the ashes in his family's possession aren't really his.
episodes.title: Head Case

episodes.synopsis: While the team is investigating the bizarre explosion of an ambulance carrying the body of a young Marine, Ducky makes a startling discovery.
episodes.title: Family Secret

episodes.synopsis: A Navy petty officer appears to have been eaten by a bear but is found to have had a prior stab wound. And things only get more bizarre from there.
episodes.title: Ravenous

episodes.synopsis: A high school student enters his classroom with a bomb strapped to his body and takes everyone hostage, demanding that his mother be brought to him.
episodes.title: Bait

episodes.synopsis: A dead Marine is found in a frozen pond, but the mystery only deepens when the bodies of three prominent South American gang members surface.
episodes.title: Iced

episodes.synopsis: The shooting death of a Pentagon cryptographer appears to be an at-home suicide until Abby learns that someone was with her at the time of death.
episodes.title: Untouchable

episodes.synopsis: A couple checking into a motel room find bloodstains and human tissue. Meanwhile, the detectives dig into Abby's past to find out who's stalking her.
episodes.title: Bloodbath

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team must race to locate Ziva when a suspect in a drug bust dies in her custody and the man's brother takes her hostage.
episodes.title: Jeopardy

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs is hurt in a terrorist explosion and winds up in a coma, during which he has flashbacks of his family's murder and his Desert Storm injury.
episodes.title: Hiatus: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: When Gibbs wakes from a coma with memory loss, the team rushes to help him recall the details of an impending terrorist attack.
episodes.title: Hiatus: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team must learn to work without Gibbs when Ziva is wanted by the FBI after she inadvertently witnesses a political assassination.
episodes.title: Shalom

episodes.synopsis: When Fornell is threatened by an escaped convict, Agent Gibbs returns to the NCIS team to investigate the convict's case history.
episodes.title: Escaped

episodes.synopsis: When a Navy lieutenant's bloody car is discovered, the team goes undercover to shed light on the missing woman's search for a perfect man.
episodes.title: Singled Out

episodes.synopsis: A routine traffic stop gets complicated when the Russian driver turns out to be connected to Homeland Security and one of Mike Franks's old cases.
episodes.title: Faking It

episodes.synopsis: A lance corporal bound for Iraq turns up dead in a vacant house. NCIS discovers the victim was first buried, then exhumed - and he had two fiancées.
episodes.title: Dead And Unburied

episodes.synopsis: Aside from being shocked by Abby's Halloween costume, the team investigates a ransom case involving a Marine's daughter and a nasty divorce.
episodes.title: Witch Hunt

episodes.synopsis: Navy and Army investigators team up to hunt clues in a suspected terrorist attack, but a CIA lead sends them to a warehouse rigged to explode.
episodes.title: Sandblast

episodes.synopsis: When a decorated Marine veteran's apparent suicide is clouded by suspicious circumstances, Gibbs makes it his mission to restore the man's honor.
episodes.title: Once A Hero

episodes.synopsis: When his sister shows up on his doorstep bloodied and disoriented, McGee breaks NCIS protocol and risks his job with an independent investigation.
episodes.title: Twisted Sister

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team must partner with the FBI when a suspected serial killer's body is found charred and mummified inside a Marine base furnace.
episodes.title: Smoked

episodes.synopsis: The team inspects a robotic, self-driving vehicle named Otto, in which a Navy lieutenant is found dead. Was it suicide or sabotage?
episodes.title: Driven

episodes.synopsis: When the body of a high-level Marine intelligence officer turns up dead in a small town motel, NCIS must step on local toes to uncover the killer.
episodes.title: Suspicion

episodes.synopsis: Wanted terrorist Mamoun Sharif is on the loose with a highly toxic chemical weapon, and NCIS must track him down before he strikes.
episodes.title: Sharif Returns

episodes.synopsis: When the Navy's top secret weapon system is stolen, the team yanks Ducky out of the autopsy room, sending him undercover to thwart an arms deal.
episodes.title: Blowback

episodes.synopsis: A young sailor's body is found in a squalid section of town and while it appears to be suicide, the team uncovers evidence pointing to murder.
episodes.title: Friends And Lovers

episodes.synopsis: When a Navy lieutenant working for the International Atomic Energy Agency contracts radiation poisoning, NCIS suspects foul play by an insider.
episodes.title: Dead Man Walking

episodes.synopsis: An explosion at a military cemetery opens a crypt full of dismembered bodies; Gibbs and team must inform the victims’ families and solve the crime.
episodes.title: Skeletons

episodes.synopsis: A frozen Marine regains consciousness on Ducky’s autopsy table, so the team retraces his steps, uncovering a secret Baghdad trip and a link to Gibbs.
episodes.title: Iceman

episodes.synopsis: An NCIS tip line call turns out to be a trap, killing two agents. Feeling personally responsible, Agent Paula Cassidy steps up to help investigate.
episodes.title: Grace Period

episodes.synopsis: When a petty officer who served as a model for one of McGee's latest book characters is murdered, all eyes turn to the horrified author for clues.
episodes.title: Cover Story

episodes.synopsis: Director Shepard's informant meeting goes awry when her contact is killed, leading Gibbs to intervene in Shepard's chase after their nemesis.
episodes.title: Brothers In Arms

episodes.synopsis: A blind photographer's unique, non-sighted senses help track a petty officer's killer; meanwhile, Gibbs and Tony deal with commitment issues.
episodes.title: In The Dark

episodes.synopsis: Turning away from a pile of bureaucratic paperwork, acting director Gibbs leaps on the case of a man found dead in a taxi bound for NCIS headquarters.
episodes.title: Trojan Horse

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs and his NCIS agents reluctantly reveal their most carefully guarded secrets during a round of Homeland Security polygraph tests.
episodes.title: Angel Of Death

episodes.synopsis: The final showdown between the NCIS team and an elusive arms dealer reaches an explosive and deadly conclusion.
episodes.title: Bury Your Dead

episodes.synopsis: While examining the body of a hit-and-run victim, Ducky makes a shocking discovery that leads to a search for a missing child.
episodes.title: Family

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs and Lt. Mann unite for a joint investigation into the murder of a Marine captain who had access to highly classified information.
episodes.title: Ex-File

episodes.synopsis: While demonstrating an autopsy on an anonymous cadaver, Ducky finds evidence of murder and a connection to a criminal mastermind.
episodes.title: Identity Crisis

episodes.synopsis: When the team tries to talk a distraught naval officer down from a rooftop, what starts out as a suicide attempt turns into a murder investigation.
episodes.title: Leap of Faith

episodes.synopsis: The team is put in mortal danger while investigating a mysterious death on a naval research ship that's been abandoned in the middle of the ocean.
episodes.title: Chimera

episodes.synopsis: When Gibbs agrees to help his deceased daughter's childhood friend, he finds himself at the center of an emotional journey into his past.
episodes.title: Requiem

episodes.synopsis: The team's investigation into the assassination of a Navy admiral takes an unexpected turn when they meet a woman searching for her missing husband.
episodes.title: Designated Target

episodes.synopsis: During a forensics lab tour, the team learns that one of McGee's Youth Rangers was abducted and has been missing for years.
episodes.title: Lost & Found

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team pays a heavy price when they try to track down a delusional Marine who escaped from a psychiatric ward.
episodes.title: Corporal Punishment

episodes.synopsis: When a Muslim Marine is found dead near a mosque, NCIS suspects murder, but the autopsy is delayed for religious reasons.
episodes.title: Tribes

episodes.synopsis: When high-tech naval radar goes missing, the NCIS team stakes out a warehouse to catch a suspected thief -- but witnesses a murder instead.
episodes.title: Stakeout

episodes.synopsis: When a Navy dog handler is found mauled to death, the team needs to determine if his dog is the killer or the victim of a canine framing.
episodes.title: Dog Tags

episodes.synopsis: When the dead body of arms dealer La Grenouille surfaces, the NCIS team is put under investigation for his murder by the FBI.
episodes.title: Internal Affairs

episodes.synopsis: When a mortar attack in Baghdad turns into a murder investigation, two members of the NCIS team are sent to Iraq to solve the case.
episodes.title: In the Zone

episodes.synopsis: Ziva's undercover assignment takes a shocking and deadly turn when the serial killer she has been tracking becomes suspicious of her.
episodes.title: Recoil

episodes.synopsis: After coming face-to-face with an evasive killer and his gun, Palmer suffers a trauma-induced memory block and can't seem to identify the shooter.
episodes.title: About Face

episodes.synopsis: A former NCIS agent is found dead. Suicide is the suspected cause of death -- until Jenny finds evidence of murder.
episodes.title: Judgment Day: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The team mourns the loss of one of their own, and their lives are on the line when Jenny's history with the deceased comes back with a vengeance.
episodes.title: Judgment Day: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs learns of a startling relationship between a homicide case involving the killing of a petty officer and Vance's decision to break up his team.
episodes.title: Last Man Standing

episodes.synopsis: While investigating an apparent suicide aboard an aircraft carrier, Tony discovers a possible connection to a larger scheme.
episodes.title: Agent Afloat

episodes.synopsis: The team learns the hazards of Washington politics when an esteemed senator asks Gibbs to solve the murder of a female naval officer.
episodes.title: Capitol Offense

episodes.synopsis: Things get a little personal when the ambush of two Marines leads the NCIS team to Gibbs's hometown, where some of his skeletons are revealed.
episodes.title: Heartland

episodes.synopsis: NCIS runs headlong into FBI interference when they look into the case of a Marine who was found tortured and murdered in his garage.
episodes.title: Nine Lives

episodes.synopsis: In the days before Halloween, a rampaging serial killer posts cryptic clues online, which the NCIS team must decipher before he strikes again.
episodes.title: Murder 2.0

episodes.synopsis: Rookie Dwayne Wilson helps NCIS investigate a bank robbery that leaves a guard dead at Quantico, the world's most heavily secured Marine base.
episodes.title: Collateral Damage

episodes.synopsis: When Vance instructs Gibbs to track down the traitor in the department, the team launches an elaborate war game designed to ferret out the mole.
episodes.title: Cloak

episodes.synopsis: To nab a crook determined to steal government secrets, the team is forced to rely on tips and information from sketchy sources.
episodes.title: Dagger

episodes.synopsis: A petty officer is killed in a car crash, but suspicious circumstances lead the agents to question whether his death was truly an accident.
episodes.title: Road Kill

episodes.synopsis: A double homicide case leads the NCIS team to a set of fingerprints that implicate a Vietnam War veteran who's been dead for almost two decades.
episodes.title: Silent Night

episodes.synopsis: When McGee enters a women's prison to investigate the murder of a guard, the inmates riot and take over, trapping him behind bars.
episodes.title: Caged

episodes.synopsis: After Ducky is stabbed during an investigation, the team uncovers decades-old secrets from the doctor's past -- including allegations of war crimes.
episodes.title: Broken Bird

episodes.synopsis: When a captain is murdered in gruesome fashion, the NCIS team uncovers surprising details about his private life, including a possible act of treason.
episodes.title: Love & War

episodes.synopsis: The murder of a Marine with a questionable past -- and a cryptic clue left at the crime scene -- forces Gibbs to confront secrets of his own.
episodes.title: Deliverance

episodes.synopsis: When one of Tony's old cases is reopened and a key witness found murdered, Gibbs hands him the reins to finally solve the case.
episodes.title: Bounce

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs gets a chance to show off his sniper skills when the murder of a fellow agent leads him to Arizona, the victim's home turf.
episodes.title: South by Southwest

episodes.synopsis: When Vance deploys the squad in his own private investigation into the death of a friend, Gibbs decides to take a closer look into Vance's past.
episodes.title: Knockout

episodes.synopsis: When an officer's son finds a gun at a playground, Gibbs and his team work to untangle a series of murders committed with the weapon.
episodes.title: Hide and Seek

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs and the rest of the NCIS team join forces with shifty CIA agent Trent Kort to bring down one of the most-wanted criminals on their watch list.
episodes.title: Dead Reckoning

episodes.synopsis: A scientist working on a top-secret government project disappears, and Abby is tapped to take over in his absence -- but will she meet a similar fate?
episodes.title: Toxic

episodes.synopsis: NCIS teams up with the Office of Special Projects in Los Angeles to investigate a murder, but the case spirals into an issue of national security.
episodes.title: Legend: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: In Los Angeles, the joint task force closes in on a terrorist sleeper cell, but Mossad operative Rivkin interferes with an agenda of his own.
episodes.title: Legend: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: When a security leak at a top-secret meeting leads to the murder of an ICE agent, NCIS teams up with the FBI and ICE to hunt down the killer.
episodes.title: Semper Fidelis

episodes.synopsis: The team follows Mossad agent Rivkin back to Israel, where Ziva meets with her father -- the head of Mossad -- in an increasingly volatile situation.
episodes.title: Aliyah

episodes.synopsis: As the hunt for Ziva's replacement begins, Gibbs and his remaining crew must get back to work with the past still weighing heavily on their minds.
episodes.title: Truth or Consequences

episodes.synopsis: The team finds that the bizarre death of a Marine and his friends may be linked to their past, but it is Gibbs who ends up traveling down memory lane.
episodes.title: Reunion

episodes.synopsis: The team must take a second look into the death of a lieutenant after the blogger who accused them of a cover-up winds up dead.
episodes.title: The Inside Man

episodes.synopsis: When a Marine's body surfaces halfway around the world, the investigation forces Ziva to dig up a buried chapter of her life.
episodes.title: Good Cop, Bad Cop

episodes.synopsis: When a Marine known for practical jokes dies on the eve of Halloween, the team finds that the victim's pranks may have roused ghoulish retribution.
episodes.title: Code of Conduct

episodes.synopsis: A murder investigation prompts Gibbs and the team to play family counselor to his former mentor in hopes of averting a bloody international conflict.
episodes.title: Outlaws and In-Laws

episodes.synopsis: With the team's help, Vance faces his demons while uncovering a complex relationship with a killer that puts his whole family in danger.
episodes.title: Endgame

episodes.synopsis: The team members literally find themselves in the dark when an investigation into the death of a lieutenant is connected to a citywide blackout.
episodes.title: Power Down

episodes.synopsis: A dead Marine's work with a government think tank leads Gibbs and the team into the life of a 12-year-old prodigy who may be the killer's next target.
episodes.title: Child's Play

episodes.synopsis: When the enlisted son of a retired colonel-turned-preacher is found dead, the team believes he may be the victim of a hate crime; Gibbs's dad visits.
episodes.title: Faith

episodes.synopsis: When a Navy pilot is found dead under odd circumstances, Gibbs and his team find themselves battling a no-nonsense attorney with a hidden agenda.
episodes.title: Ignition

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs questions DiNozzo's ability to do his job when Tony's father becomes involved in the team's investigation of an assassination plot.
episodes.title: Flesh & Blood

episodes.synopsis: When the government's star witness in an embezzlement case is targeted by an assassin, it is up to the team to help her make it home alive.
episodes.title: Jet Lag

episodes.synopsis: The team finds itself in a race against time when a terrorist group threatens to detonate a dirty bomb in the Washington area.
episodes.title: Masquerade

episodes.synopsis: When a Marine veteran is found dead, Gibbs, Fornell and the team hit the open road to bust an illegal trucking operation.
episodes.title: Jack-Knife

episodes.synopsis: Secrets are exposed when Gibbs's former mother-in-law surfaces as a witness in an investigation of her Navy captain fiancé's murder.
episodes.title: Mother's Day

episodes.synopsis: The team investigates the shooting of a Marine who had gone MIA and uncovers that he led another life that no one could have imagined.
episodes.title: Double Identity

episodes.synopsis: The team members notice similarities between themselves and their Coast Guard counterparts when a Navy diver seeking sunken treasure is found dead.
episodes.title: Jurisdiction

episodes.synopsis: The death of a Navy officer leads Gibbs and the team into the world of high-priced call girls, relying on a D.C. madam to help them catch a killer.
episodes.title: Guilty Pleasure

episodes.synopsis: The bodies of a petty officer and a mobster wash up on the beach, leading the team to a polygraph specialist who may covering up the truth.
episodes.title: Moonlighting

episodes.synopsis: DiNozzo finds himself increasingly captivated by a woman he has never met while he investigates the murder of her brother.
episodes.title: Obsession

episodes.synopsis: The team tries to track down a serial killer, while Abby heads south of the border into Mexico to deliver a speech, with McGee in tow.
episodes.title: Borderland

episodes.synopsis: When a colleague's murder sends shockwaves through the team, Gibbs uncovers a surprising link to the crime; the team learns of the rape of a sailor.
episodes.title: Patriot Down

episodes.synopsis: In Mexico, Gibbs faces his demons and meets the head of a drug cartel, bringing him to a startling decision; a prisoner dies on Tony and Ziva's watch.
episodes.title: Rule Fifty-One

episodes.synopsis: With drug cartel leader Paloma Reynosa on the loose and intent on fulfilling her vendetta, Gibbs takes desperate measures to protect his loved ones.
episodes.title: Spider and the Fly

episodes.synopsis: A young girl's kidnapping turns into much more when her grandfather complicates the investigation by working outside the law.
episodes.title: Worst Nightmare

episodes.synopsis: When the motives behind an attack on a female bomb tech link her to a murder, the team investigates her closely guarded personal life.
episodes.title: Short Fuse

episodes.synopsis: When the body of an American officer is connected to a British Navy vessel, murder turns into a volatile international incident.
episodes.title: Royals and Loyals

episodes.synopsis: When a controversial DJ and a Navy commander are shot to death on a live talk show, the team uncovers a sinister plan that involves a bomb.
episodes.title: Dead Air

episodes.synopsis: Delving into the mind of a brilliant Navy scientist, Abby becomes fixated on solving her murder; DiNozzo's fling leads to an interesting Halloween.
episodes.title: Cracked

episodes.synopsis: DiNozzo's father returns, playing a vital role in a murder investigation that could have catastrophic results.
episodes.title: Broken Arrow

episodes.synopsis: The team is assigned to protect Ziva's father when his attendance at a high-level conference leads to an unexpected turn of events.
episodes.title: Enemies Foreign

episodes.synopsis: The team scrambles for answers after a shocking ambush leaves Vance seriously injured and reveals a new twist to their current investigation.
episodes.title: Enemies Domestic

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team investigates the disappearance of a Navy petty officer who is the sole witness in an upcoming murder trial.
episodes.title: False Witness

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs and the team partner with a Coast Guard Investigative Service agent to solve the murder of a Marine gunned down on a dinner boat.
episodes.title: Ships in the Night

episodes.synopsis: A Navy recruiter's session at a college fair comes to a fatal end, prompting the team, along with Dr. Mallard's forerunner, to solve his murder.
episodes.title: Recruited

episodes.synopsis: The team springs into action to find the person responsible for beating a Marine sergeant to death in his own backyard.
episodes.title: Freedom

episodes.synopsis: The team members undergo mandatory psych evaluations while investigating the death of a commanding officer who was shot in his stateroom.
episodes.title: A Man Walks into a Bar…

episodes.synopsis: A botched assassination attempt forces the team to protect a foreign official's daughter who is studying in the U.S. and is smitten with McGee.
episodes.title: Defiance

episodes.synopsis: The dismembered fingertips and teeth of a murdered Marine are found in a pickpocket's stolen purse, launching a mission to find a coldblooded killer.
episodes.title: Kill Screen

episodes.synopsis: As a new agent joins the office, the team learns that a former employee found dead was selling details on how to rob a warehouse full of valuables.
episodes.title: One Last Score

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs questions Vance's motives when he's asked to question a teenage boy accused of killing his retired Marine father.
episodes.title: Out of the Frying Pan

episodes.synopsis: The team connects a message written in blood, left by a murdered Navy commander, to a manuscript that may contain classified military information.
episodes.title: Tell-All

episodes.synopsis: Special Agent Barrett returns to lead the investigation of a seaman's death that may be connected to a series of port-related murders.
episodes.title: Two-Faced

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team tracks a Navy lieutenant's killer after a Pentagon security camera reveals a petty officer committing the crime.
episodes.title: Dead Reflection

episodes.synopsis: When his ex-partner seems to be the victim of the Port-to-Port Killer, Tony revisits his days as a detective in Baltimore, where he first met Gibbs.
episodes.title: Baltimore

episodes.synopsis: After new evidence reveals that the Port-to-Port Killer has infiltrated the agency, the teams chase every lead in a race to track him down.
episodes.title: Swan Song

episodes.synopsis: The lives of the team are in jeopardy when they follow a trail of violence and come face-to-face with the infamous Port-to-Port Killer.
episodes.title: Pyramid

episodes.synopsis: After spending months tracking down his target, Tony is left with the blood of an NCIS agent on his hands, and it's up to Gibbs to help him.
episodes.title: Nature of the Beast

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team uncovers a startling surprise after a young Marine shows up to his homecoming party with a fatal stab wound.
episodes.title: Restless

episodes.synopsis: The line between McGee's personal and professional life is blurred when NCIS uncovers a connection between his grandmother and a lieutenant's murder.
episodes.title: The Penelope Papers

episodes.synopsis: The team searches for the person and motive behind a contract killer targeting a Navy lieutenant commander. Abby uncovers new info about her family.
episodes.title: Enemy on the Hill

episodes.synopsis: When a Coast Guard officer is gunned down on a cargo vessel, the NCIS team searches for the killer but finds something else.
episodes.title: Safe Harbor

episodes.synopsis: An NCIS case changes from accidental death to murder when evidence reveals that a Navy lieutenant died of forced over-hydration.
episodes.title: Thirst

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team searches for answers when the current husband of both Gibbs's and Fornell's ex-wife is suspiciously kidnapped.
episodes.title: Devil's Triangle

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS team uncovers a discrepancy with DNA remains when investigating the crash of a military plane that had been transporting caskets.
episodes.title: Engaged: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: As the NCIS team continues its search for a missing Marine, Gibbs and Ziva travel to her last known whereabouts in Afghanistan.
episodes.title: Engaged: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: After Anthony DiNozzo Sr. is found with a dead body in his trunk and no memory of the previous night, NCIS must figure out if he is capable of murder.
episodes.title: Sins of the Father

episodes.synopsis: When a Navy captain is killed in a hotel room, NCIS must track down and protect his pregnant companion from unknown assailants.
episodes.title: Newborn King

episodes.synopsis: The investigation into the murder of a Navy commander leads the NCIS team to E.J. Barrett's whereabouts and a new probe into Agent Stratton.
episodes.title: Housekeeping

episodes.synopsis: When a Navy lieutenant is found dead in a building under construction, NCIS searches for a killer while dealing with her distraught detective husband.
episodes.title: A Desperate Man

episodes.synopsis: During a routine stop for his morning coffee, Gibbs finds himself staring down the barrel of a gun, forcing him to question choices he has made.
episodes.title: Life Before His Eyes

episodes.synopsis: When a Navy captain is found dead wearing an unusual costume, NCIS uncovers a secret society of real-life superheroes and must track down the villain.
episodes.title: Secrets

episodes.synopsis: When a Navy psychologist is found dead, Gibbs goes face-to-face with Dr. Samantha Ryan of Psy Ops to uncover the truth behind the suspected suicide.
episodes.title: Psych Out

episodes.synopsis: Top-secret clearance from a research laboratory is jeopardized when the murder of a chief petty officer is connected to an international arms dealer.
episodes.title: Need to Know

episodes.synopsis: The secretary of the Navy partners Gibbs with Dr. Samantha Ryan after top secret information is leaked by someone on the inside.
episodes.title: The Tell

episodes.synopsis: Director Vance's brother-in-law is the lead suspect when Gibbs and the NCIS team investigate the murder of a petty officer.
episodes.title: The Good Son

episodes.synopsis: Following the murder of a Marine, Tony and Ziva join Ziva's mentor in Colombia in a search for a missing Marine lieutenant and Navy chaplain.
episodes.title: The Missionary Position

episodes.synopsis: After a warehouse fire reveals missing Navy documents, posing a potential threat to national security, NCIS joins the Baltimore P.D. investigation.
episodes.title: Rekindled

episodes.synopsis: The NCIS investigation of a fire on a Navy vessel leads to elevated security at all U.S. Navy facilities worldwide. DiNozzo and Ziva travel to Italy.
episodes.title: Playing with Fire

episodes.synopsis: NCIS analyzes what secrets could be in the hands of a terrorist targeting the Navy when a high-tech bug is found inside a probationary agent's tooth.
episodes.title: Up In Smoke

episodes.synopsis: Terrorism threatens to shake the foundations of the Navy and NCIS, as the team struggles to capture the newest member of the NCIS Most Wanted Wall.
episodes.title: Till Death Do Us Part

episodes.synopsis: As the team copes with the aftermath of the bombing, they are directed to find and terminate with extreme prejudice the terrorist responsible.
episodes.title: Extreme Prejudice

episodes.synopsis: The body of an NCIS employee turns up four months after a bombing, and each member of the team is required to undergo psychological evaluation.
episodes.title: Recovery

episodes.synopsis: Ducky revisits a case he worked years previously and uncovers a link to the team’s current investigation into the death of a Marine.
episodes.title: Phoenix

episodes.synopsis: When the crew of a helicopter that crashed at sea washes ashore days later, the NCIS team is charged with investigating the accident.
episodes.title: Lost At Sea

episodes.synopsis: While looking into the murder of a Navy officer, the team uncovers a link to a Medal of Honor recipient who was also a close friend of Gibbs’s father.
episodes.title: The Namesake

episodes.synopsis: While investigating the brutal death of an officer, Gibbs discovers the chief witness suffers from post-traumatic stress disorder.
episodes.title: Shell Shock: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs continues helping a Marine who suffers from post-traumatic stress disorder as the team works to thwart a domestic terrorist.
episodes.title: Shell Shock: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs appeals to a former contact for help locating a kidnapped girl, while Abby and Ziva work with the girl’s young friend who witnessed the crime.
episodes.title: Gone

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs and FBI Agent T.C. Fornell hunt for a shooter who tried to take out Fornell -- but their mutual ex-wife, Diane Sterling, gets involved.
episodes.title: Devil's Trifecta

episodes.synopsis: The Christmas spirit is tempered when the NCIS team begins a murder investigation that leads them to a mysterious hoard of cash.
episodes.title: You Better Watch Out

episodes.synopsis: As the team works to solve a murder involving a petty officer and a journalist, Ziva's father -- the director of Mossad -- pays her a surprise visit.
episodes.title: Shabbat Shalom

episodes.synopsis: Ziva buries her father as the team hunts down the hit man -- and the person who hired him -- responsible for the shootings at Vance's home.
episodes.title: Shiva

episodes.synopsis: Abby encounters some troubling flashbacks to her childhood when the NCIS team takes a case involving a Marine and a deadly car crash.
episodes.title: Hit And Run

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs and his team apprehend a notorious cyberterrorist but soon discover that his reach extends much further than they realized.
episodes.title: Canary

episodes.synopsis: Investigating the sudden death of a Marine, the NCIS team follows the clues to an underground fight club. Meanwhile, Vance learns some shocking news.
episodes.title: Hereafter

episodes.synopsis: Kidnappers seize Ducky and Palmer while they are transporting the body of an officer who committed suicide back to NCIS headquarters.
episodes.title: Detour

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs's barber suspects his own son may be involved in a murder, and the NCIS team suspects a Marine may have stolen a small fortune from the Navy.
episodes.title: Prime Suspect

episodes.synopsis: The wife of a dead Marine dog handler suspects a more sinister truth, and she asks Gibbs and his team to investigate.
episodes.title: Seek

episodes.synopsis: After a medical officer is murdered aboard a Navy vessel during a storm, the team uncovers a host of suspects -- including McGee's estranged father.
episodes.title: Squall

episodes.synopsis: The team looks into the plight of a Navy reservist whose husband has disappeared, and Tony worries that Ziva is planning to avenge her father's death.
episodes.title: Chasing Ghosts

episodes.synopsis: NCIS gets involved when a Massad officer causes trouble in Virginia, and Tony and Ziva head to Berlin to track the killer of Ziva's father.
episodes.title: Berlin

episodes.synopsis: Ignoring orders from their superiors to step down, the team intensifies its search for Bodnar -- and Ziva avenges her father's death.
episodes.title: Revenge

episodes.synopsis: The Department of Defense hammer comes down over NCIS's handling of the Bodnar case, with the blow falling squarely on Gibbs.
episodes.title: Double Blind

episodes.synopsis: While the rest of the team investigates the death of a SEAL, Gibbs faces intensifying scrutiny from the Department of Defense over the Bodnar case.
episodes.title: Damned If You Do

episodes.synopsis: An explosion that causes a casualty linked to the agency changes Parsons's outlook on Gibbs and the team. DiNozzo and McGee investigate as civilians.
episodes.title: Whiskey Tango Foxtrot

episodes.synopsis: Determined to locate Ziva, Tony chases leads in Israel; Gibbs and the team continue their tireless hunt for Parsa and his growing terrorist ring.
episodes.title: Past, Present and Future

episodes.synopsis: The team must rely on Twitter for a case involving a missing Navy lieutenant; McGee misplaces his badge but doesn't tell Gibbs and the authorities.
episodes.title: Under The Radar

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs and McGee travel to Afghanistan when a murder case leads them to an Afghan women’s shelter Mike Frank has secretly supported for years.
episodes.title: Anonymous Was a Woman

episodes.synopsis: DiNozzo revisits his Baltimore Police Department days when he spots a felony suspect from an old case at the crime scene of a murdered petty officer.
episodes.title: Once a Crook

episodes.synopsis: The group partners with the Coast Guard Investigative Service to probe a suspicious explosion on an oil rig; a prankster targets team members.
episodes.title: Oil & Water

episodes.synopsis: After Gibbs leaves mid-case to help his father reconnect with a former war pilot, Tony and McGee argue over who should run lead on the investigation.
episodes.title: Better Angels

episodes.synopsis: When an FBI agent-turned-lawyer confides in Gibbs, the team must re-examine a hit-and-run murder case; McGee grows suspicious of Tony’s odd behavior.
episodes.title: Alibi

episodes.synopsis: After learning the secretary of the Navy was bugged during a confidential briefing, the NSA analyst who predicted the security breach joins the team.
episodes.title: Gut Check

episodes.synopsis: The team discovers a link between a murder victim and the boyfriend of Diane Sterling, Gibbs and Fornell's ex-wife; a new analyst adjusts to NCIS.
episodes.title: Devil's Triad

episodes.synopsis: When a mystery illness strikes children from military families, the team investigates and helps medical researchers; Vance struggles with forgiveness.
episodes.title: Homesick

episodes.synopsis: When a stolen drone leads to an elusive terrorist, NCIS teams with the Department of Defense, including Gibbs's former girlfriend.
episodes.title: Kill Chain

episodes.synopsis: Hunting for a terrorist, the team finds one of his cohorts using evidence from the drone attack. Emotionally shaken, McGee deals with the aftermath.
episodes.title: Double Back

episodes.synopsis: The murder of a port authority officer reveals Parsa's possible whereabouts; Bishop discloses her past association with the elusive terrorist.
episodes.title: Monsters and Men

episodes.synopsis: After finding faulty bulletproof vests in a cache of stolen USMC gear, the team tries to locate the source and any vests already shipped to soldiers.
episodes.title: Bulletproof

episodes.synopsis: When DiNozzo is investigated in the death of a man impersonating an officer, the one eyewitness is DiNozzo's dad, who is in town to disclose a secret.
episodes.title: Dressed To Kill

episodes.synopsis: After a bomb detonates at a military charity concert, the team must determine if the target was a washed-up rocker or if a larger scheme was in play.
episodes.title: Rock and a Hard Place

episodes.synopsis: When the body of a New Orleans politician and ex-NCIS agent washes ashore, the two field offices unite to uncover the motive and reveal the killer.
episodes.title: Crescent City: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Gibbs and Special Agent Pride chase leads in New Orleans after evidence points to a copycat serial killer; Bishop sends DiNozzo a special souvenir.
episodes.title: Crescent City: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: After returning to the Department of Defense, McGee's girlfriend finds a break in a controversial case; DiNozzo advises McGee about his love life.
episodes.title: Page Not Found

episodes.synopsis: The team must ascertain if an officer's murder was the result of a bar fight or because he knew too much; DiNozzo and McGee start a juice cleanse.
episodes.title: Alleged

episodes.synopsis: The team investigates the disappearance of a photographer who was scheduled to testify at an Army court-martial hearing.
episodes.title: Shooter

episodes.synopsis: DiNozzo is given an assignment to bring an admiral's daughter home from Paris, but he turns to the team when he enters a controversial crime scene.
episodes.title: The Admiral's Daughter

episodes.synopsis: NCIS investigates a fire on a ship that served as a secret detention site for terrorists; Gibbs returns to his childhood home after his father dies.
episodes.title: Honor Thy Father
